message.text:
𝐀𝐭𝐭𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, 𝐏𝐀𝐓𝐀𝐦𝐬! 📩

Open your inboxes as PATA Philippines FEU Student Chapter has finally sent out emails via Outlook to all our aspiring executive committees! 

Be sure to keep your notifications on, check your mails, and carefully follow through the instructions provided as you take your next step towards your student leadership roles! May this strengthen your drive to lead and keep you focused in your journey towards excellence with PATA. 

We cannot wait to see you shine and make a difference. Best of luck, future PATAms! 💙

Caption by: Jea Madronio
Pubmat by: Layza Tolomia

#PATAPHFEU

𝐀𝐭𝐭𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, 𝐏𝐀𝐓𝐀𝐦𝐬! 📩

Open your inboxes as PATA Philippines FEU Student Chapter has finally sent out emails via Outlook to all our aspiring executive committees! 

Be sure to keep your notifications on, check your mails, and carefully follow through the instructions provided as you take your next step towards your student leadership roles! May this strengthen your drive to lead and keep you focused in your journey towards excellence with PATA. 

We cannot wait to see you shine and make a difference. Best of luck, future PATAms! 💙

Caption by: Jea Madronio
Pubmat by: Layza Tolomia

message.text:
𝐈𝐭’𝐬 𝐂𝐡𝐢’𝐬 𝐃𝐚𝐲! 🎊

On this special day, we celebrate the day of the 𝐃𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐫 𝐨𝐟 𝐋𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐥𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐋𝐞𝐠𝐚𝐥 𝐀𝐟𝐟𝐚𝐢𝐫𝐬 𝐃𝐞𝐩𝐚𝐫𝐭𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭, 𝐌𝐱. 𝐂𝐡𝐢 𝐌𝐚𝐫𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐞𝐳 𝐒𝐮𝐚𝐯𝐢𝐥𝐥𝐨—your kindness, and the positivity you always bring to everyone around you. 💖

May you enjoy your 𝐂𝐇𝐈-𝐫𝐫𝐢𝐟𝐢𝐜 𝐃𝐚𝐲 with full of love and light you truly deserve. ✨🩷

From your ITHM Student Council family, we send you our warmest greetings and best wishes for a wonderful year ahead. 🎉

Caption by: Chelsea Ann Menor

On this special day, we celebrate the day of the 𝐃𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐫 𝐨𝐟 𝐋𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐥𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐋𝐞𝐠𝐚𝐥 𝐀𝐟𝐟𝐚𝐢𝐫𝐬 𝐃𝐞𝐩𝐚𝐫𝐭𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭, 𝐌𝐱. 𝐂𝐡𝐢 𝐌𝐚𝐫𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐞𝐳 𝐒𝐮𝐚𝐯𝐢𝐥𝐥𝐨—your kindness, and the positivity you always bring to everyone around you. 💖

May you enjoy your 𝐂𝐇𝐈-𝐫𝐫𝐢𝐟𝐢𝐜 𝐃𝐚𝐲 with full of love and light you truly deserve. ✨🩷

From your ITHM Student Council family, we send you our warmest greetings and best wishes for a wonderful year ahead. 🎉

Caption by: Chelsea Ann Menor

On this special day, we celebrate the day of the 𝐃𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐫 𝐨𝐟 𝐋𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐥𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐋𝐞𝐠𝐚𝐥 𝐀𝐟𝐟𝐚𝐢𝐫𝐬 𝐃𝐞𝐩𝐚𝐫𝐭𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭, 𝐌𝐱. 𝐂𝐡𝐢 𝐌𝐚𝐫𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐞𝐳 𝐒𝐮𝐚𝐯𝐢𝐥𝐥𝐨—your kindness, and the positivity you always bring to everyone around you. 💖

May you enjoy your 𝐂𝐇𝐈-𝐫𝐫𝐢𝐟𝐢𝐜 𝐃𝐚𝐲 with full of love and light you truly deserve. ✨🩷

From your ITHM Student Council family, we send you our warmest greetings and best wishes for a wonderful year ahead. 🎉

Caption by: Chelsea Ann Menor

#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil

message.text:
𝐈𝐭’𝐬 𝐂𝐡𝐢’𝐬 𝐃𝐚𝐲! 🎊

On this special day, we celebrate the day of the 𝐃𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐫 𝐨𝐟 𝐋𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐥𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐋𝐞𝐠𝐚𝐥 𝐀𝐟𝐟𝐚𝐢𝐫𝐬 𝐃𝐞𝐩𝐚𝐫𝐭𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭, 𝐌𝐱. 𝐂𝐡𝐢 𝐌𝐚𝐫𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐞𝐳 𝐒𝐮𝐚𝐯𝐢𝐥𝐥𝐨—your kindness, and the positivity you always bring to everyone around you. 💖

May you enjoy your 𝐂𝐇𝐈-𝐫𝐫𝐢𝐟𝐢𝐜 𝐃𝐚𝐲 with full of love and light you truly deserve. ✨🩷

From your ITHM Student Council family, we send you our warmest greetings and best wishes for a wonderful year ahead. 🎉

Caption by: Chelsea Ann Menor

#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil
